<li id="cite_note-212"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-212">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160701214200/http://www.eskimo.com/~recall/bleed/0303.htm">"Our Daily Bleed..."</a> Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.eskimo.com/~recall/bleed/0303.htm">the original</a> on July 1, 2016<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">January 28,</span> 2008</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Our+Daily+Bleed...&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eskimo.com%2F~recall%2Fbleed%2F0303.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARacism+in+the+United+States" class="Z3988"></span></span>
